@startuml
title Retry behavior

participant "ExportNewsMessageHandler" as Handler
queue "RabbitMQ" as Rabbit
participant "MinIO / S3" as S3
database "NewsRepository" as NewsRepo

alt S3 temporary failure
    Handler -> S3: write chunk
    S3 --> Handler: throws runtime/storage exception
    Handler -> Rabbit: nack all messages with original exception
    Rabbit -> Rabbit: apply retry policy
else missing news
    Handler -> NewsRepo: find by ids
    NewsRepo --> Handler: some ids missing
    Handler -> Rabbit: nack missing messages with UnrecoverableMessageHandlingException
    Rabbit -> Rabbit: no retry for missing-news messages
end

@enduml
